thread.title: Stephanie
thread.title_full: White Mountain Puzzles reviewed by Stephanie

author: Stephanie
title: Stephanie
text: The puzzles themselves are absolutely gorgeous, and we have framed several and put them up in our home. The quality is wonderful, and they are neither too difficult nor too easy to accomplish. They make for a great hobby with something lovely to show for your effort.
